 Galvatron looked ahead. He heard the comm. He made a decesion. The destrons 
had to in this war no matter what position he held or what his missions 
where. Whoever this magmatron was he would serve him. But if betrayed him he 
would not let him live to gloat about it. He continued on his root.

--part1_4b.5fce212.278f9fba_boundary
